    "Gradientbased methods and generative approaches, including feature collision, are explored in deep learning.",
    "Passive and active defense approaches are studied along with their complexities and limitations to mitigate poisoning attacks.",
    "In conclusion, further research directions are identified to address poisoning attacks in machine learning (Table 1).A.",
    "Shafee and T. A. Awaad [53] studied privacy threats in machine learning, specifically deep learning, highlighting issues and limitations in existing countermeasures.",
